OL,3,CSadiq Khan intervenes in row over Tube
OL,4,Cstation book stand removal
OL,6,FThe Mayor has stepped in to reverse a
OL,7,Fdecision by Transport for London to
OL,8,Fremove all free book swap stands from
OL,9,Fits Tube stations over fire safety
OL,10,Ffears.
OL,12,FTfL had begun removing books from
OL,13,FLondon Underground stations on the
OL,14,Fadvice of the London Fire Brigade
OL,15,F(LFB), which found book libraries to
OL,16,Fbe a fire hazard.
OL,18,FA spokesperson from LFB said: "This is
OL,19,Fdue to combustible material posing a
OL,20,Ffire safety risk if it is stored on
OL,21,Fthese premises.
