OL,3,CSadiq Khan intervenes in row over Tube
OL,4,Cstation book stand removal
OL,6,F"Non-subsurface stations have been
OL,7,Fasked to remove book libraries from
OL,8,Fdisplay until they have the correct
OL,9,Ffire safety plans in place."
OL,11,FThe move sparked criticism among book
OL,12,Flovers, who said the stalls were an
OL,13,Fimportant part of the community, while
OL,14,Ffire safety experts also said the
OL,15,Fmeasure was disproportionate.
OL,17,FThe criticism has prompted an
OL,18,Fintervention from the Mayor, who is
OL,19,Fchair of TfL.
