OL,3,CSadiq Khan intervenes in row over Tube
OL,4,Cstation book stand removal
OL,6,FA source close to Sadiq Khan told ITV
OL,7,FNews London: "The Mayor has stepped in
OL,8,Fand we are looking to reverse this
OL,9,Fdecision as soon as possible. TfL are
OL,10,Fworking urgently with LFB to ensure
OL,11,Fthis happens."
OL,13,FKamal Shah is the chair of North
OL,14,FHarrow Community Library, which is run
OL,15,Fentirely by volunteers.
OL,17,FAccording to him, station book stands
OL,18,Fhelp encourage reading and improves
OL,19,Faccess to books.
