OL,3,CSadiq Khan intervenes in row over Tube
OL,4,Cstation book stand removal
OL,6,FHe said: "Books cost a lot of money.
OL,7,FPeople haven't got the money now to
OL,8,Factually buy these books.
OL,10,F"Some of the books we have, they're
OL,11,Fpristine and there's no point putting
OL,12,Fthem in recycling or landfill ...
OL,13,Fstations have a large amount of
OL,14,Ffootfall.
OL,16,F"So that is why this place is probably
OL,17,Fmore important in terms of getting
OL,18,Faccess to books than any of the other
OL,19,Forganisation places."
