OL,3,CSadiq Khan intervenes in row over Tube
OL,4,Cstation book stand removal
OL,6,FFormer LFB officer and fire and
OL,7,Fresilience consultant Steve Dudeney
OL,8,Falso questioned TfL's the reasoning
OL,9,Fbehind removing the libraries in the
OL,10,Ffirst place.
OL,12,FHe said: "These book swaps have been
OL,13,Fin place for a long time now.
OL,15,F"Why have they only just become a
OL,16,Fproblem? What is the precedent? I'm
OL,17,Fnot aware that there's been a fire
OL,18,Finvolving them.
