OL,3,CSadiq Khan intervenes in row over Tube
OL,4,Cstation book stand removal
OL,6,F"It just seems that someone's come
OL,7,Falong, seen that one thing as a
OL,8,Fproblem and nothing else as a problem.
OL,9,FAnd I don't think that makes sense."
OL,11,FMr Dudeney added that fire risk
OL,12,Fassessment needs to look at cost and
OL,13,Fbenefit: "Inevitably, a bookshelf, a
OL,14,Fsmall bookshelf - they're about the
OL,15,Fsize of a washing machine from what
OL,16,FI've seen - that does present a hazard.
