OL,6,F"But when you look at the risk of that
OL,7,Fhazard starting a fire, it's
OL,8,Fnegligible because it's in an open
OL,9,Farea, it's monitored, there's fire
OL,10,Fdetection systems there, there's
OL,11,Fpeople walking past all day."
